n private equity and credit investing prior to founding centerbridge in partnership with jeffrey h aronson in october  mr gallogly was with the blackstone group for  years at blackstone he was most recently a senior managing director the head of private equity and a member of the firm’s management and investment committees throughout his  year career in investing and finance mr gallogly has been involved in a broad spectrum of industries businesses and investment cycles mr gallogly served on president obama’s council on jobs and competiveness from  to  and the president’s economic recovery advisory board from  to  he also currently serves on the advisory council of the hamilton project an economic policy group at the brookings institution the columbia business school board of overseers and the board of trustees of the roads charter schools he is a partner of the partnership for new york city and member of the council on foreign relations and the economic club of new york mr gallogly graduated with honors from the university of notre dame and attended sophia university in tokyo he received his mba from columbia business school in  mr gallogly lives in new york city with his wife and three daughters contact media inquiries kriston mcintoshphone  kmcintoshbrookingsedu your email… sign up all content   the hamilton project terms and conditions mark t gallogly  centerbridge investor login new york new york  park avenue new york ny     contact us registered with the united states securities and exchange commission iardcrd number  get directions x london london  new burlington street nd floor london ws be      contact us authorized and regulated by the uk financial conduct authority registration number  link to uk stewardship code get directions x menu investor login new york new york  park avenue new york ny     contact us registered with the united states securities and exchange commission iardcrd number  get directions x london london  new burlington street nd floor lon